title: Fiesta Chicken & Kūmara-Sprout Toss with Garlic Aioli
description: Get ready to turn mealtime into a culinary fiesta with this firecracker dish! Tender chicken steaks have been marinated in Mexican spices for unparalleled levels of flavour and are served alongside roasted kūmara and Brussels sprouts for a meal you won’t want to miss.
